### HTML Email Template for Reserved Gift

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reserved Gift</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Container Styles */
       .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Header Styles */
       .header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Content Styles */
       .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Button Styles */
       .button {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Button Hover Styles */
       .button:hover {
            background-color: #555;
        }

        /* Text Styles */
       .text {
            color: #666;
        }

        /* Color Scheme */
        :root {
            --primary-color: #333;
            --secondary-color: #666;
            --accent-color: #f7dc6f;
        }

        /* Typography */
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--secondary-color);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Container -->
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Reserved Gift</h1>
        </div>
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Dear [Name],</h2>
            <p>We are pleased to inform you that your reserved gift is ready for collection. Please find the details below:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Gift Name: [Gift Name]</li>
                <li>Collection Date: [Collection Date]</li>
                <li>Collection Time: [Collection Time]</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Please note that the gift will be available for collection during the specified time. If you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact us.</p>
            <button class="button">Collect Gift</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

### CSS Variables (Custom Properties)

The template uses CSS variables to define the color scheme and typography. You can modify these variables to suit your brand's style.

*   `--primary-color`: The primary color of your brand (used for headings and buttons).
*   `--secondary-color`: The secondary color of your brand (used for body text and links).
*   `--accent-color`: The accent color of your brand (used for highlights and emphasis).

### Customization

To customize the template, you can modify the following elements:

**HTML Promotional Email Template**

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reserved Gift Notification</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Container Styles */
       .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Header Styles */
       .header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Content Styles */
       .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Button Styles */
       .button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* Button Hover Styles */
       .button:hover {
            background-color: #3e8e41;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Reserved Gift Notification</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Dear [Customer Name],</h2>
            <p>We are pleased to inform you that the gift you reserved has been set aside for you.</p>
            <p>Here are the details of your reserved gift:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Gift Name: [Gift Name]</li>
                <li>Gift Description: [Gift Description]</li>
                <li>Gift Price: [Gift Price]</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Please find the attached invoice for your reserved gift. We will contact you once the gift is ready for pickup.</p>
            <a href="[Invoice URL]" class="button">View Invoice</a>
            <p>Thank you for choosing us!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
```

**Variables to Replace:**

* `[Customer Name]`: The customer's name
* `[Gift Name]`: The name of the reserved gift
* `[Gift Description]`: A brief description of the reserved gift
* `[Gift Price]`: The price of the reserved gift
* `[Invoice URL]`: The URL of the attached invoice

**Note:** This template uses basic HTML and CSS styles. You can customize it according to your brand's design and preferences.
